messages.content: ComfyUI_Segment_Mask is a project that is a ComfyUI version of the Segment Anything project by Facebook Research.
What is the original Segment Anything project?
The original Segment Anything project is a repository located at https://github.com/facebookresearch/segment-anything, which was created by Facebook Research.
Is ComfyUI_Segment_Mask related to the ComfyUI-Impact-Pack?
Yes, ComfyUI_Segment_Mask is related to the ComfyUI-Impact-Pack, which can be found at https://github.com/ltdrdata/ComfyUI-Impact-Pack.
